English

=======================

MP3 download here:  http://kiwi6.com/file/gktwnm3kgu

=======================

Just like every suite i composed, I always to put a music work call "Special feature" or also call "Special credit " or as "SF " and "SC" in final ,it's like the movie or TV shows ening credit. usually this kind of music will be some popular music or some very easy making music works, 

but this thime. this SF is the hardest work and most high quality in all the "Canterlot legend series" music. listen to the muisc in the epic mood and ending this music series. 

"Halo of Equestria symphony" this is the movie theme music i composed for the "Star wars pony", i do wish we can have this , and this is also tribute to maste John Williams ,the composer I most liked and the who composed the great Star wars music

the music is actually a suite itself, and combine with 9 themes, even it has some part is the melody i preserve form the orginal melody from star wars , but still most of all melody and the structure are my own composed, 

this is the most hard working piece i ever done in this whole series, but i glad i did it, i also put a artwork i did for this music video. i will show it when it comes out. 


please share it to your friends if you like it. may the force be with you and we will see you next music time

goodbye~

Sean.M 

==========================

中文

=======================

MP3 開放下載點於此:  http://kiwi6.com/file/gktwnm3kgu

=======================

就跟我所有組曲作品一樣，我會在組曲的最後放一個「特別收錄曲」叫做「Special feature」或「Special Credit」簡稱「SF」或「SC」，概念類似電影的片尾曲，通常特別收錄曲都是簡單的改編曲、輕鬆的流行音樂或是些隨手作作的小品音樂

但是這次不一樣，這首特別收錄曲是坎特拉傳奇全曲中最用心、最細緻、結構最龐大的曲子，讓我們在輝煌氣氛下跟這組曲系列告別

「阿奎斯堤亞星環交響曲」

這首音樂是為了小馬版的星際大戰而寫的主題曲，也同時向我尊敬的約翰‧威廉斯大師致敬，他為星際大戰寫出了傳奇千古的主題曲

這首曲子同時包含了九個主題，然後最主要的主題是小馬的主題和星際大戰主題的融合，也終於完成了我第一首以小馬主題為主的大型交響曲，其中還有些小小片段有保留他原本的旋律，主要是向大師致敬，但是整曲的主要旋律和結構配器等都還是自己作的

為了這首音樂，我還特地自己繪製一張圖放在影片之中，希望大家喜歡，但也希望大家喜歡音樂，記得分享給朋友、按讚和訂閱頻道，非常的感恩你們的支持

願以後能創作更多音樂給大家
我們下次再見

親王
